  title: Ancient Flower
  entry: Today's expidition went well. The ancient flower, Archaefructus was found
    down here intact. Very suspicious that such a flower can be alive a thousand
    feet underground. Our party has heard a few weird shrieks but nothing more. I
    do miss my husband.
